longBusinessSummary: The Victory Bancorp, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for The Victory Bank that provides commercial and consumer banking products and services for small and middle market commercial and retail customers in Montgomery County, Pennsylvania. The company offers checking accounts, savings and money market accounts, escrow management and interest on lawyer trust accounts, demand deposits, investment certificates, and certificates of deposit (CD); CD account registry and insured cash sweep services; secured and unsecured personal term loans and lines of credit; home mortgages; home equity lines of credit; and revolving credit, small business, and automobile loans. It also provides commercial term loans, commercial lines of credit, commercial mortgage/real estate loans, and construction loans; and government banking, remote deposit, mobile banking, online banking and bill pay, cash management, merchant services, e-statement, and lock box services, as well as cards. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Limerick, Pennsylvania.
